name: Owl decorations
description:
Set of 12 coloured hanging wooden owls, perfect for twiggy trees or anywhere! Add a little woodland magic to your home x
Each owl measures 5 x 4cm.

name: Huggie Baby in blue plush fabric
description:
This piece of gorgeousness is my own design of a lovely little huggie baby.
Made in the softest pale blue plush fabric with a little wisp of brown hair.
They measure 21cm from top to bottom, perfect for little hands to hold and hug.
They can be personalised with hand embroidery on the back  with any single name to make them the perfect gift. (please leave details of this on your paypal transaction).
This item is CE marked making them suitable from birth x
